"""Generates ui/src/trace_processor/pfgraph_query_builder.ts from the
pfgraph JSON schema (docs/design-docs/pfgraph-schema.json).

Run from the repo root:
  python3 tools/gen_pfgraph_query_builder

This ensures the TypeScript query builder stays in sync with the schema.
When a new operation is added to the schema, re-run this script. If the
new operation uses a complex $ref type that the generator doesn't know
how to render, it will fail with a clear error message.
"""

